>>9	byte	22	WordPerfect graphic image
>>9	byte	23	WordPerfect hyphenation code
>>9	byte	24	WordPerfect hyphenation data
>>9	byte	25	WordPerfect macro resource data
>>9	byte	27	WordPerfect hyphenation lex
