2       string  EYWR    AmigaWriter file

# chi:  file(1) magic for ChiWriter files
0       string          \\1cw\          ChiWriter file
>5      string          >\0             version %s
0       string          \\1cw           ChiWriter file

# Quark Express from https://www.garykessler.net/library/file_sigs.html
